00:32:28,580 --> 00:32:30,060
I should be the one saying sorry.

573
00:32:30,300 --> 00:32:31,780
You are so busy and tired every day.

574
00:32:31,900 --> 00:32:33,460
But all I did was do as I pleased

575
00:32:33,580 --> 00:32:35,340
and followed you around
like I was your tail.

576
00:32:35,700 --> 00:32:36,460
I'm sorry.

577
00:32:37,620 --> 00:32:38,860
I won't do that anymore.

578
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:42,460
Ruanruan.

579
00:32:44,100 --> 00:32:44,860
Ruanruan.

580
00:33:21,820 --> 00:33:22,820
[Yunshen]
(I was busy.)

581
00:33:22,900 --> 00:33:23,900
(I didn't check my phone.)

582
00:33:24,660 --> 00:33:26,060
(I have to go to Malaysia.)

583
00:33:26,420 --> 00:33:28,660
(I might be too busy
to answer your call.)

584
00:33:28,940 --> 00:33:30,260
(You can leave me messages on WeChat.)

585
00:33:31,380 --> 00:33:32,460
(Don't miss me too much.)

586
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:35,780
(But I will certainly miss you a lot.)

587
00:33:42,980 --> 00:33:44,180
(Granny is sick.)

588
00:33:45,060 --> 00:33:46,020
(It's very serious.)

589
00:33:47,180 --> 00:33:48,620
(I don't know what to do.)

590
00:33:58,540 --> 00:33:59,140
(Alright.)

591
00:33:59,660 --> 00:34:00,700
(I'll be waiting for you.)

592
00:34:01,380 --> 00:34:02,460
(Take good care of yourself.)

593
00:34:21,700 --> 00:34:22,460
Mr. Fu and Mr. Fu Jr.

594
00:34:22,620 --> 00:34:23,660
I am Mr. Xie's secretary.

595
00:34:23,980 --> 00:34:24,940
- Good to see you.
- Me too.

596
00:34:25,020 --> 00:34:26,220
How are the patients doing?

597
00:34:26,500 --> 00:34:27,700
Just elementary school kids.

598
00:34:27,860 --> 00:34:28,620
Nothing serious.

599
00:34:28,780 --> 00:34:30,340
They're under observation
at the hospital.

600
00:34:30,420 --> 00:34:32,180
We did that
to appease consumers as well.

601
00:34:33,260 --> 00:34:34,340
Let's head to the company first.

602
00:34:34,420 --> 00:34:35,820
Mr. Xie prepared a meal

603
00:34:36,220 --> 00:34:37,820
to welcome both of you.

604
00:34:37,940 --> 00:34:39,020
- Go to the hospital first.
- Go to the hospital first.

605
00:34:42,380 --> 00:34:44,420
It's not a life-threatening illness.

606
00:34:44,540 --> 00:34:46,540
The priority now is to solve this matter

607
00:34:46,620 --> 00:34:47,460
and make up for the loss.

608
00:34:47,540 --> 00:34:49,260
Mr. Xie has been too worried
to even sleep.

609
00:34:49,740 --> 00:34:52,060
I finally get why public opinion
has been leaning to one side.

610
00:34:52,620 --> 00:34:54,420
We are here to solve this matter.

611
00:34:54,700 --> 00:34:55,740
The hospital first.

612
00:34:58,060 --> 00:34:58,860
This way, please.

613
00:35:08,820 --> 00:35:09,460
Zhu Jiu.

614
00:35:10,100 --> 00:35:12,060
Why are you here so early
in the morning?

615
00:35:12,140 --> 00:35:14,060
What is it that you couldn't tell me
on the phone?

616
00:35:14,140 --> 00:35:15,460
Come on. Let's talk inside.

617
00:35:15,540 --> 00:35:17,220
I still need to make breakfast
for your cousin.

618
00:35:17,260 --> 00:35:17,820
Aunt.

619
00:35:18,540 --> 00:35:19,620
I'll talk to you here.

620
00:35:20,180 --> 00:35:22,580
Yang can't know about this.

621
00:35:23,580 --> 00:35:25,180
What is it?

622
00:35:27,220 --> 00:35:28,260
Granny...

623
00:35:31,820 --> 00:35:33,100
Granny has liver cancer.

624
00:35:33,620 --> 00:35:34,660
It is in the late stage.

625
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:37,460
Cancer?

626
00:35:38,340 --> 00:35:39,580
What should we do?

627
00:35:41,740 --> 00:35:43,220
How much is that going to cost?

628
00:35:44,700 --> 00:35:46,180
What should we do, Zhu Jiu?

629
00:35:46,260 --> 00:35:47,820
You're a doctor. You should know.

630
00:35:47,980 --> 00:35:50,500
Cancer treatment costs a lot of money.

631
00:35:51,380 --> 00:35:52,820
Will selling the house be enough?

632
00:35:55,620 --> 00:35:57,260
I doubt we can keep your granny's

633
00:35:57,780 --> 00:35:59,100
small courtyard house.

634
00:35:59,220 --> 00:35:59,860
Aunt.

635
00:36:01,140 --> 00:36:02,940
Don't worry about the medical expenses.

636
00:36:03,660 --> 00:36:04,660
I will take care of it.

637
00:36:05,140 --> 00:36:06,660
I didn't come here to ask you

638
00:36:07,260 --> 00:36:09,540
to share the medical expenses either.

639
00:36:09,900 --> 00:36:11,420
That's how it should be anyway.

640
00:36:12,300 --> 00:36:13,220
All these years,

641
00:36:13,500 --> 00:36:14,460
your granny

642
00:36:14,940 --> 00:36:16,540
spent all her money sending you abroad.

643
00:36:16,820 --> 00:36:19,100
We didn't take any money from her.

644
00:36:20,900 --> 00:36:21,540
Aunt.

645
00:36:22,260 --> 00:36:25,540
Don't tell Granny about this yet.

646
00:36:25,940 --> 00:36:27,860
Okay, I know. I won't.

647
00:36:28,180 --> 00:36:29,260
It's a serious illness.

648
00:36:29,540 --> 00:36:31,540
It would be a great shock to her.

649
00:36:33,340 --> 00:36:34,740
What else did the doctor say?

650
00:36:35,740 --> 00:36:37,340
Can you spare some time today

651
00:36:37,780 --> 00:36:39,940
to meet her attending doctor with me
at the hospital?

652
00:36:40,500 --> 00:36:41,780
Sure.

653
00:36:42,020 --> 00:36:44,020
Nothing is more important

654
00:36:44,140 --> 00:36:46,020
than your granny's illness now.

655
00:36:46,140 --> 00:36:48,220
I will ask for a leave of absence
with my superior later.

656
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:49,780
After Yang has gone to school,

657
00:36:49,940 --> 00:36:51,180
I'll go meet you at the hospital.

658
00:36:52,140 --> 00:36:52,540
Okay.

659
00:36:52,740 --> 00:36:54,060
See you at the hospital later.

660
00:36:54,820 --> 00:36:56,060
I have to go back and cook.

661
00:37:10,740 --> 00:37:11,820
Use it to soothe your eyes.

662
00:37:12,540 --> 00:37:13,260
Look at you.

663
00:37:13,700 --> 00:37:15,420
You look like Ultraman
with your swollen eyes.

664
00:37:20,740 --> 00:37:21,300
Ruanruan.

665
00:37:21,660 --> 00:37:22,820
Do you want to hear a joke?

666
00:37:36,620 --> 00:37:39,740
Once upon a time,
two tomatoes were walking on the street.

667
00:37:40,300 --> 00:37:42,940
They kept walking and walking.

668
00:37:43,460 --> 00:37:45,140
Suddenly, a car whizzed by.

669
00:37:45,380 --> 00:37:46,300
It flew across

670
00:37:46,740 --> 00:37:48,460
and flattened one of the tomatoes.

671
00:37:49,380 --> 00:37:50,140
What do you think

672
00:37:50,380 --> 00:37:52,580
the other tomato said?

673
00:37:54,460 --> 00:37:55,140
It said,

674
00:37:55,620 --> 00:37:58,060
"Why have you turned into ketchup?"

675
00:38:01,980 --> 00:38:03,780
I have another one.
Do you want to hear it?

676
00:38:14,900 --> 00:38:16,060
I'm sorry, Ruanruan.

677
00:38:17,620 --> 00:38:19,420
I guess I'm really a boring person.

678
00:38:20,100 --> 00:38:21,420
I can't even tell a proper joke.

679
00:38:27,220 --> 00:38:29,300
The joke earlier
was pretty funny, right?

680
00:38:29,700 --> 00:38:32,020
I find you funny.

681
00:38:40,060 --> 00:38:40,860
Okay, no more jokes.

682
00:38:41,140 --> 00:38:41,580
Well...

683
00:38:42,140 --> 00:38:43,700
It's all because of that lame joke.

684
00:38:44,340 --> 00:38:45,100
I won't tell it again.

685
00:38:46,340 --> 00:38:47,060
Zhizhi.

686
00:38:48,180 --> 00:38:50,460
I find myself so pathetic.

687
00:38:52,260 --> 00:38:56,260
I feel like I have been begging someone
for happiness.

688
00:38:56,940 --> 00:38:57,700
It's not like that.

689
00:38:57,780 --> 00:38:58,820
Don't think that way.

690
00:38:59,860 --> 00:39:00,540
Fu Xizhou...

691
00:39:01,900 --> 00:39:02,700
He's just not good

692
00:39:02,820 --> 00:39:04,580
at expressing his feelings.

693
00:39:06,300 --> 00:39:07,060
Don't overthink it.

694
00:39:07,180 --> 00:39:07,620
Hush now.

695
00:39:08,860 --> 00:39:10,420
I don't want to wait for him anymore.

696
00:39:18,380 --> 00:39:19,020
Ruanruan.

697
00:39:19,820 --> 00:39:21,180
You are still emotional now.

698
00:39:22,340 --> 00:39:23,540
Don't jump to conclusions.

699
00:39:23,660 --> 00:39:24,220
Okay?

700
00:39:24,660 --> 00:39:25,380
Zhizhi.

701
00:39:26,380 --> 00:39:27,260
You know what?

702
00:39:28,140 --> 00:39:31,500
The two of us talked it out seriously
the other day.

703
00:39:32,380 --> 00:39:33,660
I kept saying

704
00:39:33,820 --> 00:39:35,660
that there should be honesty and trust

705
00:39:36,540 --> 00:39:37,340
between spouses.

706
00:39:38,660 --> 00:39:40,860
But I didn't mention love at all.

707
00:39:42,020 --> 00:39:43,500
Because I was afraid.

708
00:39:43,740 --> 00:39:45,820
I was afraid to ask if he loved me.

709
00:39:45,940 --> 00:39:47,740
I was afraid to know the answer.

710
00:39:48,580 --> 00:39:50,180
Fu Xizhou, that jerk!

711
00:39:51,460 --> 00:39:52,260
Once he gets back,

712
00:39:52,580 --> 00:39:53,980
I will teach him a good lesson.

713
00:39:57,060 --> 00:39:58,300
I want to leave him.

714
00:40:11,660 --> 00:40:12,260
Please come in.

715
00:40:30,220 --> 00:40:31,020
Hi, Sam.

716
00:40:31,460 --> 00:40:32,300
I'm Yunshen.

717
00:40:33,540 --> 00:40:35,060
I apologize for everything

718
00:40:36,300 --> 00:40:37,380
that you went through.

719
00:40:37,540 --> 00:40:38,540
You are?

720
00:40:41,540 --> 00:40:44,940
Your child received
our company's vaccine.

721
00:40:45,140 --> 00:40:46,180
I'm so sorry

722
00:40:46,260 --> 00:40:47,460
for what he suffered

723
00:40:47,580 --> 00:40:48,980
and for making you worried.

724
00:40:49,060 --> 00:40:50,380
Is your vaccine fake?

725
00:40:51,060 --> 00:40:52,780
If anything happens to my son,

726
00:40:53,180 --> 00:40:55,300
I will not let you get away with it.

727
00:41:03,660 --> 00:41:04,900
I'm very sorry.

728
00:41:06,620 --> 00:41:08,380
But the vaccine is not fake.

729
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,220
We are investigating

730
00:41:10,740 --> 00:41:12,100
the reason why it failed.

731
00:41:12,740 --> 00:41:14,220
And we will give you an answer.

732
00:41:14,380 --> 00:41:17,300
Who knows if your words can be trusted?

733
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:26,580
Aside from
the child's hospital expenses,

734
00:41:26,740 --> 00:41:28,380
this is additional compensation

735
00:41:28,580 --> 00:41:31,300
that Lingtian Pharmaceutical
is giving the child.

736
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:32,580
Contact me at any time.

737
00:41:32,660 --> 00:41:33,740
What do you mean by this?

738
00:41:33,860 --> 00:41:34,940
Don't take it wrong.

739
00:41:35,060 --> 00:41:36,860
It's just something
that we want to do for you.

740
00:41:37,060 --> 00:41:40,340
I want an answer. Not this money.

741
00:41:45,580 --> 00:41:47,540
We will have an answer for everyone.

742
00:41:47,700 --> 00:41:50,380
Just give us a little time.

743
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:53,220
I hope you do what you promised.

744
00:41:56,700 --> 00:41:58,260
Okay. We won't bother you anymore.

745
00:42:01,140 --> 00:42:01,780
Goodbye.

746
00:42:13,780 --> 00:42:15,740
I will check the hospital's
refrigeration conditions

747
00:42:15,900 --> 00:42:18,540
and get the doctor's medical records.

748
00:42:19,340 --> 00:42:20,500
I will meet Mr. Xie

749
00:42:20,820 --> 00:42:21,820
to get relevant information.

750
00:42:22,420 --> 00:42:23,020
Okay.

751
00:42:56,820 --> 00:43:00,420
♪I see you in a dark corner♪

752
00:43:00,700 --> 00:43:04,060
♪With vulnerability overwhelming you♪

753
00:43:04,300 --> 00:43:06,380
♪Biting your lips
and facing away from me♪

754
00:43:06,620 --> 00:43:10,620
♪You break the walls of stubbornness♪

755
00:43:11,460 --> 00:43:14,420
♪Once more, another sundown
swiftly passes by♪

756
00:43:14,700 --> 00:43:19,860
♪Love is like a lie at the end
of the century♪

757
00:43:20,020 --> 00:43:25,780
♪That almost fools me♪

758
00:43:35,660 --> 00:43:42,260
♪A kiss can heal this wrecked world♪

759
00:43:42,580 --> 00:43:49,220
♪If there is a slight possibility
of avoiding loneliness♪

760
00:43:49,500 --> 00:43:55,900
♪Let me endure the heavy rainfall
with you♪

761
00:43:56,180 --> 00:44:00,220
♪If there is a slight possibility♪

762
00:44:00,460 --> 00:44:06,340
♪The moon that once shone for me
should stay radiate♪

763
00:44:06,660 --> 00:44:12,460
♪You'll regain happiness
when you are true to yourself♪

764
00:44:21,940 --> 00:44:28,900
♪You feel my pain♪

765
00:44:29,020 --> 00:44:35,980
♪No reason for those meaningless winds
to pass by me♪

766
00:44:36,220 --> 00:44:42,900
♪When the meaningless things hit me♪

767
00:44:50,780 --> 00:44:57,260
♪Why must we miss out on each other
when our hearts are broken?♪

768
00:44:57,940 --> 00:45:04,540
♪Imitating others who flinch and escape
after love sparks fade away♪

769
00:45:04,700 --> 00:45:13,540
♪All I yearn for
is the warmth deep within you♪
